user is greeted with welcome page and "Let's get started!" button

basic:
User is presented a form.

User can select toppings from checkbox.
User can select size from dropdown menu or radio button.
Current price displayed at all times.

User hits Order pizza button, page says thank you!

stretch:

webpage displays an image of a pizza with nothing on it.
user is presented icons of toppings to choose from. clicking on an icon removes it from selection and adds topping to pizza's array and to pizza image.
user can select size from dropdown menu or radio buttons, selection will change the size of the pizza image.
when user hits Order pizza button, a confirmation screen will show, displaying final price and all of the user's choices in text and/or image , and ask user to confirm.

stretch stretch:

order multiple pizzas
have premade pizzas as options.